  "body": "### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Be a member of a group chat.\r\n2. Send a non-mention message to the group chat.\r\n3. Check the display of the unread indicator.\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\nThe unread counter is shown instead of an unread badge for non-mention messages in the group chat.\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/c8d8aee5-3d69-495e-9856-e90716581b57)\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/407c6f58-fd62-4675-8c37-379fc0354142)\r\n\r\nAn unread badge should be displayed instead of the unread counter for non-mention messages in the group chat, indicating the presence of new unread messages.\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/7KIYbhoqNGAIFonE0w9TDz/Messages-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=1424-342207&mode=design&t=gmnAl5Vb0rMg8CJ9-0\r\n",
